316
00:17:32,398 --> 00:17:33,697
Benarkah?

317
00:17:33,698 --> 00:17:37,397
Tapi, teman-temanku ada di sini bersamaku hari ini!

318
00:17:37,398 --> 00:17:39,197
Conan!

319
00:17:39,198 --> 00:17:41,798
Aku membawa Dokter.

320
00:17:43,998 --> 00:17:45,597
Tolong beritahu dia juga, Dok,

321
00:17:45,598 --> 00:17:49,297
