393
00:20:53,098 --> 00:20:54,697
Benar.

394
00:20:54,698 --> 00:20:58,097
Apa? Hei, hei, kenapa bisa ada darah di sana?

395
00:20:58,098 --> 00:20:59,497
Aku penasaran.

396
00:20:59,498 --> 00:21:01,597
Oh, itu mungkin karena...

397
00:21:01,598 --> 00:21:03,597
Ushigome...

398
00:21:03,598 --> 00:21:06,997
Ushigome melukai jarinya.

399
00:21:06,998 --> 00:21:08,297
Terluka?

400
00:21:08,298 --> 00:21:11,097
Mungkin jarinya terluka karena pecahan kerang atau semacamnya

401
